@*
    ADR-006 (2026-05-05) -- subdomain tenant routing.

    Override of Volo.Abp.Account.Pro.Public.Web's tenant-switcher view component.
    Tenancy is resolved EXCLUSIVELY from the URL subdomain
    (CurrentUserTenantResolveContributor + DomainTenantResolveContributor in
    CaseEvaluationAuthServerModule.ConfigureMultiTenancy). Showing a tenant
    switcher would invite users to attempt cross-tenant navigation, which
    the resolver chain refuses to honor. Hiding the UI surface keeps the
    affordance honest.

    File path mirrors the original embedded view path so this override
    takes precedence at runtime. Empty body = no rendered output.

    Cross-reference:
    - docs/decisions/006-subdomain-tenant-routing.md
    - https://community.abp.io/posts/hide-the-tenant-switch-of-the-login-page-4foaup7p
*@
